name: MY BODY IS READY TO CUTE DEAATH (White Text)
description:
For those of you who didn't manage to get one at the first show:

The FIRST OFFICIAL CUTE DEATH SHIRT.

WITH THE NAME OF THE BAND SPELLED WRONG.


(x_n ) Design by Johnny PK Starstorm.
( =_+) Modelling by Stefano Black Earth.

( 1_1) Photography by BEAN.

☭ ☭ ☭ ☭ ☭ ☭ ☭


When you buy CUTE DEATH, three things happen:

* Your entire Appearance tree levels up once, while your Optimism skill under the Personality tree gets a permanent -4 modifier

* Your entire arm will instantly, permanently turn solid black and take on the texture of gorilla, as you can see from the store photographs

* The terrorists lose

* Your mom stops having sex forever

* God exists

* God looks at the world and spits on his mistake

* Your girlfriend comes back

* No she doesn’t

* You are alone

* We hate you

* please by a shirt

*//3

name: MYSTERY GIFT from ☮☮☮☮☮ Johnny PK Starstorm
description: Have you ever wondered what it would be like to be Johnny Weiss? Well keep wondering but you can own something from Johnny Weiss! For a small fee, you too can have a Super Secret Mystery Prize from Johnny that will come with a personalized note. You may get an old shirt or maybe a good book...hell you might get a sick drawing who knows?! buy it and find out, come on no one is watching. *** When you order, make sure to contact us and tell us your name, and anything else you want, for your personalized note.

name: A DAY IN THE LIFE of ☠☠☠☠☠ StefanoBlack▒
description: Have you ever wondered what it would be like to be Stefano? Do you even *want* to live? For a modest emotional-damages surcharge, you too can fly just a bit too close to the sun: For ONE ENTIRE DAY (your choosing), Stefano will bombard you with endless texts, Facebook messages, Twitter DMs, Tumblr asks, ironic Foursquare check-ins, fictional Yelp reviews - and maybe even his only weakness, a PHONECALL - telling you his innermost thoughts throughout the day, with a guarantee of no filter or social tact whatsoever. *** When you order, make sure to contact us and let us know by what means you prefer to have your privacy liberated, and how to reach you on each medium. And prepare to know regret.
